{
  "stem": "20142.7",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And you can imagine the-- the-- what condition were in the toilets and the cleaning quarters without any water, and how people had to release them in the worst cases, on the staircases and corners and so on.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was very depressing condition.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And you really didn't care anymore whether this is the end of the life or just escape to-- to something else.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But we knew that sooner or later, it would not last very long.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "With the-- under condition like this, no human being can exist.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And finally, after two days, with some calm restored and some promises made and some provision given us, with a quarter of a-- a round bread, they packed us up in railroad trains and-- without mercy, packing us up to a point of just standing one to-- one-- one to another.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Because there was no space to sit down or-- or-- there again, there-- there were no sanitary provisions made by Germans.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And packed up and-- I think that cattle would have been treated with a better condition than the human being was treated at that time.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were-- the entire transport of some 10 people-- 10 wagons of people packed up to-- to a maximum.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think that in a wagon like this there were between 100, 125 people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were just standing room only.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And everybody was grasping for air coming through the two openings on both sides of the wagon.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the door were closed, sealed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the train finally, sometime in the afternoon, left.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And on the way, we were passing such places as Siedlce.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when I have seen the sign, 'Siedlce,' the-- it's a little town between Warsaw and Treblinka-- I knew that we are on our way to Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
